description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for Visual Survival Guide

App offers quizzes and tutorials  to help you learn Visual Survival Guide

App is continuously updated based on your feedback.Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.

App Tools include search .



Includes following tutorials:

Introduction,
Planning and Survival Kits,
Signaling Techniques,
Psychology of Survival,
Ropes and Knots,
Basic Survival Medicine,
Medical Emergencies,
Bones and Joint Injury,
Environmental Injuries,
Types of Shelters,
Water Procurement,
Firecraft,
How to Build a Fire,
How to Light a Fire,
Food Procurement,
Desert Survival,
Tropical Survival,
Cold Weather Survival,
Sea Survival,
Expedient Water Crossings,
Field Expedient Direction Finding,
Dangerous Insects and Arachnids,
Venomous Snakes and Lizards,
Various Construction Lashings.


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on Signaling Technique,
Quiz on Type of Knots,
Quiz on Type of Shelters,
Quiz on Types of Fire.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
